name: Colors in your Eyes
description: The way I see the world to get the essence of the scenes. There are lots of colors in life and surroundings and I think there is a unique color which represents the scene so I choose when I take a shot the photography on the spot. It means no after editing is there in this to make it different from the original file. The color shows my view at the moment. Photo was taken from the view of Tate Modern in Jan. 2020 before Covid-19 rules the world. Format_PNG  Size : 4,555 x 3,037
